      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know. everything just feels so heavy lately. i look at my kids and i see how much they're already struggling with work and their own lives, and then there's me. just another thing they have to worry about, another thing they have to manage. i feel like i'm just a burden to everyone now.",
