      "content": "it's just not just about being tired. i'm getting older, i'm getting slower, and i can see the look on my daughter's face every time she has to help me with something small. it breaks my heart. i hate that my existence is making their lives harder. it feels like i'm just taking up space and energy that they need for themselves.",
